column5: Went 4 for 6 on kings today. Biggest about 18-20 and the smallest at around 12.      Bowen Sandercock Reelhard Charters
Riveting report, I was on the edge of my seat for the whole account. Oh, you're chartering now... I see. -Brian
Nice kings i can't wait to get out and get me a couple of them  Rob
Good call Brian..     Contact Roy for advertising details.  G

Were you out fishing for your own pleasure today or did you have a paying customer?  If you were pleasure fishing, congrats on the nice fish!!!   Now let's talk aboot that Spammy sig that's too large anyway...
